---
title: Seared Sirloin Steak with Garlic Herb Butter, Chive Mashed Potatoes, and Honey Roasted Carrots
description: Hankering for a plate of good ol’ steak and potatoes? We’ve got your back. This recipe takes the classics above and beyond with a few flavorful twists. There’s seared steak, creamy chive-flecked mashed potatoes, and honey-roasted carrots. And then there’s the pan sauce. Here, demi-glace and garlic herb butter mingle with the fond--the crispy bits and drippings left by the steak--to create a rich elixir you’ll want to drizzle over everything. And now you can!
